                    "source": "Change this if wrong verses are being linked, e.g. you want \"Gen 1,1-3\" but output is text from verses 2-4 → set this to -1",
                    "target": "如果链接的经文不正确，请更改此项，例如你想要“Gen 1,1-3”但输出的是第2-4节的文本 → 将此设为 -1"
