                },
                {
                    "type": "CallExpression",
                    "name": "setDesc",
                    "source": "Special prefix that will be inserted in front of the first line only, right after the \"Line prefix\". Handy for callouts. (Only applied when Put each verse on a new line? is set to true)",
                    "target": "仅插入在第一行前面的特殊前缀，紧跟在“Line prefix”之后。适合用于提示/强调。（仅当“Put each verse on a new line?”设为 true 时生效）"
                },
                {
                    "type": "CallExpression",
                    "name": "setDesc",
                    "source": "Should space be inserted between verses? (Only applied when Put each verse on a new line? is set to false. Useful for languages such as Chinese.) See also each verse postfix setting for more options.",
                    "target": "经文之间是否插入空格？（仅当“Put each verse on a new line?”设为 false 时生效。对中文等语言很有用。）另见“每节经文后缀”设置以获取更多选项。"
                },
                {
                    "type": "CallExpression",
                    "name": "setDesc",
                    "source": "This is the symbol that will be used between chapter number and verse number when copying one verse. For example \".\" → Gen 1.1.",
                    "target": "复制单节经文时，用于章号和节号之间的符号。例如“.” → Gen 1.1。"
                },
                {
                    "type": "CallExpression",
                    "name": "setDesc",
                    "source": "This is the symbol that will be used between chapter number and verse number when copying multiple verses. For example \",\" → Gen 1,1-3.",
                    "target": "复制多节经文时，用于章号和节号之间的符号。例如“,” → Gen 1,1-3。"
                },
                {
                    "type": "CallExpression",
                    "name": "setDesc",
                    "source": "Input full paths from the root vault folder to folders containing Bible translations, each translation on separate line. An example of one entry: \"Bible/NIV/\". The plugin will search for corresponding Bible files using given paths as starting points. Make sure there are no duplicate files in given paths, otherwise it is hard to tell what the output will be. The first translation will be considered your main translation.",
                    "target": "输入从库根文件夹到包含圣经译本的文件夹的完整路径，每个译本一行。示例：“Bible/NIV/”。插件会以给定路径为起点搜索对应的圣经文件。请确保给定路径中没有重复文件，否则输出结果难以判断。第一个译本将被视为你的主译本。"
                },
                {
                    "type": "CallExpression",
                    "name": "setDesc",
                    "source": "Choose what translations should be linked when copying a verse.",
                    "target": "选择复制经文时要链接的译本。"
                },
                {
                    "type": "CallExpression",
                    "name": "setDesc",
                    "source": "You can specify conversions that will be applied to the visible book name alias. For example, if you put in \"3J:3 John\", the output will be changed from \"[[3 John-01#v1|3J 1.1]]\" to \"[[3 John-01#v1|3 John 1.1]]\". The format used is \"From:To\", each entry on it's own line. TIP: ChatGPT (or similar AI tool) will probably be able to help you when creating the input.",
                    "target": "你可以指定应用于可见书名别名的转换。例如，输入“3J:3 John”，输出会从“[[3 John-01#v1|3J 1.1]]”变为“[[3 John-01#v1|3 John 1.1]]”。使用格式为“From:To”，每条单独一行。提示：在创建输入时，ChatGPT（或类似 AI 工具）可能会帮上忙。"
                },
                {
                    "type": "CallExpression",
                    "name": "setDesc",
                    "source": "You can specify conversions that will be applied to the used book name when searching for text of a verse. For example, if you put in \"Gn:Gen\", the input \"Gn 1,1\" will work even when the file is called \"Gen 1,1\". The format used is again \"From:To\", each entry on it's own line, and will be used by the plugin when the search fails using the unchanged input. Multiple entries can have same result mapping, for example you can use \"G:Gen\" and \"Gn:Gen\".",
                    "target": "你可以指定在查找经文文本时应用于所用书卷名称的转换。例如，如果你输入 \"Gn:Gen\"，输入 \"Gn 1,1\" 即使文件名为 \"Gen 1,1\" 也能正常工作。所用格式仍为 \"From:To\"，每条一行，当使用未更改的输入搜索失败时将由插件使用。多个条目可以映射到相同结果，例如你可以使用 \"G:Gen\" 和 \"Gn:Gen\"。"
                },
                {
                    "type": "CallExpression",
                    "name": "setDesc",
                    "source": "This is the separator that will be used when linking, e.g. if you enter '#' here, output will be [[Gen 1#1]]. If you are using headings to mark verses, use '#'. If you are using block references, use '^'.",
                    "target": "这是链接时使用的分隔符，例如你在这里输入 '#'，输出将为 [[Gen 1#1]]。如果你使用标题标记经文，请用 '#'. 如果你使用块引用，请用 '^'。"
                },
                {
                    "type": "CallExpression",
